&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hsuly4psyzj216g0u0n0t.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/Otb6eBHF8</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/Otb6eBHF8</guid><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:20:22 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author><category>疾病风险预报</category></item></channel></rss>